Name: athena-panel-wrapper
Summary: Runs panel and confirms user desire to logout
Copyright: GPL
Group: User Interface/Desktops

Requires: athena-gnome-core

%description
The panel-wrapper program runs panel (from athena-gnome-core) as a
subprocess.  When panel exits with status 0, indicating a user logout
requet, panel-wrapper puts up a dialog confirming the user's desire to
log out, and restarts panel if the user elects not to log out.
